  <p class="ko" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">출처: J. 웰스 와일더(J. Welles Wilder), 『New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems』(1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin"(SSRN 워킹페이퍼, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); 2020년 10월~2021년 4월 비트코인 랠리 및 2021년 5~7월, 2023년 3~10월 박스권 관련 가격 데이터.</p>
  <p class="en" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources: J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (SSRN working paper, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); price data for Bitcoin's October 2020-April 2021 rally and its May-July 2021 and March-October 2023 ranges.</p>
  <p class="ja" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">出典: J.ウェルズ・ワイルダー(J. Welles Wilder)、『New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems』(1978年); David Mesíček、"Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin"(SSRNワーキングペーパー、2026年、SSRN ID 5598690); 2020年10月~2021年4月のビットコインの上昇相場、および2021年5~7月・2023年3~10月のボックス圏に関する価格データ。</p>
  <p class="es" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Fuentes: J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (working paper de SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); datos de precio del rally de Bitcoin de octubre de 2020 a abril de 2021 y de los rangos de mayo-julio de 2021 y marzo-octubre de 2023.</p>
  <p class="de" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Quellen: J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (SSRN-Working-Paper, 2026, SSRN-ID 5598690); Preisdaten zu Bitcoins Rallye von Oktober 2020 bis April 2021 sowie den Handelsspannen von Mai-Juli 2021 und März-Oktober 2023.</p>
  <p class="fr" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources : J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978) ; David Mesíček, « Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin » (working paper SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690) ; données de prix sur le rallye du Bitcoin d'octobre 2020 à avril 2021 et ses fourchettes de mai-juillet 2021 et mars-octobre 2023.</p>
  <p class="pt" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Fontes: J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (working paper do SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); dados de preço do rali do Bitcoin de outubro de 2020 a abril de 2021 e de suas faixas de maio-julho de 2021 e março-outubro de 2023.</p>
  <p class="tr" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Kaynaklar: J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (SSRN çalışma raporu, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); Bitcoin'in Ekim 2020-Nisan 2021 rallisi ile Mayıs-Temmuz 2021 ve Mart-Ekim 2023 aralıklarına ilişkin fiyat verileri.</p>
  <p class="vi" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Nguồn: J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (working paper SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); dữ liệu giá về đợt tăng giá Bitcoin từ tháng 10/2020 đến tháng 4/2021 và các biên độ tháng 5-7/2021, tháng 3-10/2023.</p>
  <p class="id" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sumber: J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (working paper SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); data harga reli Bitcoin Oktober 2020-April 2021 serta rentang Mei-Juli 2021 dan Maret-Oktober 2023.</p>
  <p class="pl" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Źródła: J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (working paper SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); dane cenowe dotyczące rajdu Bitcoina z października 2020-kwietnia 2021 oraz przedziałów z maja-lipca 2021 i marca-października 2023.</p>
  <p class="it" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Fonti: J. Welles Wilder, New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (working paper SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); dati di prezzo relativi al rally di Bitcoin di ottobre 2020-aprile 2021 e ai suoi range di maggio-luglio 2021 e marzo-ottobre 2023.</p>
  <p class="ru" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Источники: Дж. Уэллс Уайлдер (J. Welles Wilder), New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems (1978); David Mesíček, "Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin" (рабочий доклад SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 5598690); данные о цене биткоина за период ралли октябрь 2020 - апрель 2021 года и за диапазоны май-июль 2021 и март-октябрь 2023 года.</p>
  <p class="zh" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">資料來源：J. 威爾斯·懷爾德（J. Welles Wilder），New Concepts in Technical Trading Systems（1978）；David Mesíček，「Evaluating the Parabolic SAR Strategy on Bitcoin」（SSRN 工作論文，2026，SSRN ID 5598690）；比特幣 2020 年 10 月至 2021 年 4 月漲勢，以及 2021 年 5-7 月與 2023 年 3-10 月區間之價格資料。</p>

